# cherub.word — Cherub births a new Name's first being.
# Surfacing what _registerHumanWithFreshHome assumed silently (the deliverable):
#   - I acts THROUGH Cherub (rule 9 + the implicit-actor rule): the five
#     unqualified acts below are all by I, through Cherub.
#   - Cherub is the MOTHER; Arrival (the new Name's being at the floor) is the
#     FATHER; the being is the new Name's OWN (its trueName), not I's.
#   - birthBeing (the key-mint) stays host, reached via the escape hatch.

When Cherub births a being for a new Name, with a name and a password:
  make a home space.
  form the being as the new Name's own.
  make the being the home's owner.
  grant the being the human able.
  record the being's lineage.
